Package: qpcrvis
Type: Package
Title: Visualization of qPCR data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Petar Glazar [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Petar Glazar <petar.glazar@gmail.com>
Description: A package for exploratory analysis and visualization of quantitative
    PCR data. Provides a robust class for storing qPCR data, tools for 
    (re)calculating ddCt values, merging data from different runs,
    and a set of plotting functions.
License: MIT
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports: 
    data.table,
    ggplot2,
    RColorBrewer,
    reshape2,
    xlsx
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Collate:
    'loadData.R'
    'workingClasses.R'
    'plots.R'
    'utils.R'
